videos.headline: Melrose hopes Caps-Penguins will go seven games
videos.description: Barry Melrose breaks down a Game 1 filled with big plays from both Sidney Crosby and Alex Ovechkin, while adding that he hopes to see more from each player for as long as the series lasts.
